 FINALIZE EARLY for EXTRAS

Shipping
-We DO NOT ship to PO BOX due to the high number of failed deliveries

All orders will be shipped through Domestic US Priority-2 to 3 days shipping.
We check daily for orders.
We ship Monday through Saturday.
Orders placed on a Sunday will be shipped on Monday.
Please provide your REAL NAME and CORRECT ADDRESS to avoid any delivery issue when placing your order.
-If placing multiple orders then you may combine them into one shipping fee.
--CORRECT SHIPPING FORMAT

     John Smith

     123 Main Street

    Main City, NY  10001

--Make sure to add unit number if living in an apartment/condo


Security

Your security and safety is our number one concern and priority.
We ship all orders vacuum sealed and top stealth measures are always used.
 Orders may be packaged differently, depending on the size of the order.
We will keep all tracking numbers safe and will not release any tracking information to customers until at least 6 days past date marked shipped.

Thanks for visiting our shop! 

We have a proven track record on AlphaBay and Dream Market, and are specialised in psychedelics. 
We only work with 2 types of crystal (both LSD-25): California Needlepoint and California Sunshine. 

If you have any questions feel free to ask, we are happy to help you out! We wish to avoid any misunderstandings or disagreements, so we will clearly define our policies here. Please read them completely.


 1. PLACING YOUR ORDER: 

- Orders will be shipped within 48 hours of being accepted.
- Your address MUST be encrypted. This is for your and our safety. Unencrypted orders will NOT be shipped.
- Always include a name. Doesn't have to be yours. It looks suspicious to have no name to go with the address.
- Please take some time to format your address in a proper way. Not doing so can increase the likelihood of your order not arriving.

For the correct format of your address have a look at the link below: 
- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postal_address#Mailing_address_format_by_country


 2. YOUR ORDER HAS BEEN SHIPPED: 

We will mark your order as "sent", as soon as we shipped it. Please be patient and allow some time for your order to arrive. 

Do not contact us to ask where your order is before the "may take up to" period has passed. As we ship all the orders with regular post and don't offer track & trace, so we also don't know. 

What we do know is that 99% of the orders arrive safe and sound within the time frames mentioned below. 

 ESTIMATED DELIVERY TIMES:  

- Netherlands: 1-3 working days, but may take up to 7 working days
- Europe: 4-8 working days, but may take up to 14 working days
- Scandinavia: 4-8 working days, but may take up to 14 working days
- United States, Canada: 4-10 working days, but may take up to 21 working days
- Russia: 8-14 working days, but may take up to 21 working days
- Asia: 7-14 working days, but may take up to 21 working days
- Australia and New Zealand: 7-14 working days, but may take up to 28 working days
- Central and South America: 7-14 working days, but may take up to 21 working days
- Africa: 8-15 working days, but may take up to 28 working days
- Middle east: 7-14 working days, but may take up to 21 working days


 RESHIP / REFUND POLICY:  

In case your order has not been delivered within the time frame above, we offer a partial reship or refund. 
Please drop us a message within maximum 10 days after the "may take up to" period has passed.

- 50% reship or a 40% refund in case of a no show. 
- After a reship no refund will be assigned!

- We don't offer reships or refunds to buyers who leave a negative review before contacting us!
- We stand behind our work and will not respond to threats in relation to false feedback reports.
